              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Criminel, by 4PM Games, is a noir detective mystery video game, emerging from the murderous streets of 19th-century Paris.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "In Criminel, players must solve a series of chilling murders set among the smoky streets, hotels and dark alleys of turn of the century Paris. With a prototype camera and notepad in hand, players must use the very first forensic techniques invented to help uncover the secrets that will unravel a conspiracy, solve the case and reveal the killer. The game features AAA visuals and audio, and a gripping thriller-based storyline.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Find out more at criminelgame.com.",
